data.description: This 2-story townhome is in the Madison Place community. Inside, you are welcomed by a spacious foyer. Down the hallway the home opens into the Living Room, Dining area and kitchen allowing you room to entertain family or guests. The kitchen features granite counters, and stainless steel appliances that is great for cooking family meals. Upstairs enjoy a spacious master suite with two additional bedrooms and a full bath. To relax head out back to a fully fenced backyard. In addition, enjoy Community amenities such as the pool and playground.
